<dl id="n38029b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38029b">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38029b"> 29(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Yeravda (gaol)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>The Arrest of Gandhi</b> <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> A communiquea issued by the Bombay Government on the arrest of Gandhi states: / &ldquo;Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi was arrested this morning and has been placed in the Central Prison at <mark>Yeravda</mark>.<font color="green">[&hellip;]</font>&rdquo; <small> <a name="MP6may30" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#MP6may30"><cite title="source">Morning Post</cite></a> (6 May 1930) 15/1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
